  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Prospective, multicenter, observational registry designed to collect data on syncopal
      relapses in patients undergoing pacemaker implantation for bradyarrhythmic syncope.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Prospective, multicenter, observational registry designed to collect data on syncopal
      relapses in patients undergoing pacemaker implantation for bradyarrhythmic syncope. All
      consecutive patients aged ≥18 years who underwent pacemaker implantation for syncope of
      bradyarrhythmic aetiology (proven or presumed) at participating centers from January 2010 to
      December 2013 were enrolled in the registry. During follow-up the occurrence of the first
      syncopal relapse after pacemaker implantation is recorded.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
